Ricky ran into the room, really excited to read the real ring he had found. Right away, he knew it was special. He ran his fingers around the edges and felt a rush of energy. He wanted to run outside and show it off, but he knew it was best to keep it safe in his room. He thought about what he could do with it and decided to create a game for his friends. They would take turns trying to guess the right words that started with 'R' like "really", "right", "run", “room”, “read”, and “real”
